{
  "stem": "16106.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I want to give him some sandals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said, will you run home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Will you run home right now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I came running home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, we had no idea what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My mom said, why don't you go-- I mean, just the idea when somebody's young and so nothing is going to happen to that person-- why don't you go to the estate to the-- and ask for where my father is?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, honestly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- I-- I went there and-- and asked stupid questions and was thrown out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was not-- [INAUDIBLE] what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When did you learn the truth?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We learned the truth, but we didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We learned the truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew the truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we choose not to believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who wants-- can believe that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the people were picked up on the streets and disappeared, we called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a certain [BACKOUND NOISE]  little car, the little truck, we saw it coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was when they [NON-ENGLISH] the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took them out to the-- to the-- [NON-ENGLISH] or where-- where they were then executed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Latvians were enormously active in that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a pilot called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a wonder-- the hero of Latvia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a head of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the Latvian ice hockey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very happy to get rid of the Russians and [INAUDIBLE] they received the Germans with flowers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they waved from the thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, they were extremely happy to deliver us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't-- they showed what they thought of us all the time at that point.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had no chance to hide anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
